      "type": "verse",
      "lines": [
        "### 354 Mbe! Basare Tugashya",
        "**1**",
        "Mbe! Basare tugashya tugana hakurya;",
        "Nidusakirana n’umuraba,",
        "Har’aho gutsik’ubwato,",
        "Ku cyambu gituje cyane.",
        "**Gusubiramo Ibice bya 1,2 na 3:**",
        "Ku cyambu gi-hora gitekanye iteka,",
        "I-wacu mw’ijuru hahora hatuje!",
        "Ku cyambu gituje, hahor’amahoro!",
        "(Hahor’amahoro.)",
        "**2**",
        "Twe kurangamir’inyungu z’igihe gito,",
        "Nta mumaro zifite haba namba!",
        "Dushak’aho dutsika,",
        "Ku nkombe hakury’iwacu.",
        "**3**",
        "Yesu ni we Nyenyeri itumurikira,",
        "Kandi ni w’udukingir’umuraba.",
        "Tyo twerekez’ubwato,",
        "kuri Yesu Murengezi.",
        "**4**",
        "N’ubw’ubukana bw’inyanja bwakara gute!",
        "Urusaku rukaba rwinshi cyane!",
        "Ntacyo ruzadutwara,",
        "Yes’azaruducyahira.",
        "**Gusubiramo Igice cya 4:**",
        "Mw’ijuru n’iwacu hakurya ku cyambu",
        "Mw’ijuru mw’ijuru ni ho tuzibera.",
        "Mw’ijuru heza pe! Mw’ijuru n’iwacu",
        "(mw’ijuru n’iwacu)."
      ],
      "number": 1
    }
  ]
}